  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Taijutsu (Strike)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 11</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 10</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 28 | <b>Successes:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 16 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 36</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> F, Mas, Mob</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You must be moving at Speed Rank 10 to use this technique, and the weapon used must be sheathed. You make a lightning-quick Iaijutsu-style attack, making a single attack roll against all creatures in the area, against which they must make a Spot check (DC 40) or lose their Dexterity bonus to Defense. The attack deals four times normal damage, and creatures hit must make a save or be pushed back a number of feet equal to the damage taken, rounded to the nearest 5 ft unit.<br><br>Once the attack finishes, the weapon used is unsheathed. If the weapon is not of mastercraft or higher quality, it shatters and cannot be repaired. This technique cannot be used more than once per encounter.</p>\n\n\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The second and fourth steps each increase the uses per encounter by one.</p>\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
